  <brief_title>Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Efficacy, Pharmacokinetics (PK) Interactions and Safety of Dolutegravir Plus 2 Nucleoside Reverse Transcriptase Inhibitors (NRTIs) in HIV‐1‐Infected Solid Organ Transplant Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pilot Single‐Arm Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Efficacy, PK Interactions and Safety of Dolutegravir Plus 2 NRTIs in HIV‐1‐Infected Solid Organ Transplant Patients</official_title>
