  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aims of this study are to obtain pharmacokinetic data on interactions between
      dolutegravir (DTG) and immunosuppressant drugs (Cyclosporine A, Tacrolimus, Sirolimus and
      Mycophenolic acid) in solid organ transplant (SOT) recipients to provide proof of principle
      data that DTG plus 2 nucleosides (NUCs) is safe and effective in HIV-infected SOT recipients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
